'''Betty''' is the owner of [[Betty's Magic Emporium]] in [[Port Sarim]]. She is the only character selling [[Eye of newt|eyes of newt]] in [[free-to-play]] [[Server|worlds]].

Betty plays a vital role in the [[Witch's Potion]] [[Quests|quest]], and is a character in [[The Hand in the Sand]] quest helping in the creation of [[pink dye]].

